{"tid":1572822,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"建議：增設用家將其他用家分類功能","createTime":"2019-09-15T18:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T12:14:54.000Z","uid":22047,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6cbce7eb5a8763d8898ec78b9a579e2a9dd9395f","tid":1572822,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:53:45.000Z","msg":"因啱啱有狗扮岳義士朋友：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1572796\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1572796</a><br />\n<br />\n鑑於三毛同Mon post狗橫行連登，風向容易被帶走，而最大問題呢堆人可以隨時改名。我地冇可能記低哂佢地嘅user ID，但如果block咗佢地，我地睇唔到comment，就反駁唔到，風向就會咁帶走咗，提示唔到其他user。<br />\n<br />\n我懇請連尼住增設自行分類功能，可以俾每個用家為其他用家分類（好似mac嘅tag功能咁），以顏色為基礎，佢地每一個post/reply都會highlight佢地嘅名俾用家辨認返佢嘅分類。<br />\n<br />\n分類只會係用家自己設定，其他用家係睇唔到另一用家嘅分類。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位覺得有用！"},{"pid":"d21a4ac26eb99436a881640816e375d8a020ee85","tid":1572822,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:55:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"760c2075f1b512eb5b60dfc7640de3a37dd5ca1a","tid":1572822,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R4oZup8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR4oZup8.jpg&h=22278f49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=d3afe5df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=Vjn4Al6Q2mdpb7%2BU1BdqDhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=e610cd10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"e5e41fb436f0c591066f4fb32bcd7fa2b87c0b2d","tid":1572822,"uid":22047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:56:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78c702108e4a8c8839bec097f2420e55820dc28d","tid":1572822,"uid":22047,"like":0,"